OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FOutbreaks of
OL,6,Frain spreading east across the region
OL,7,Fto reach Kent in the early hours. The
OL,8,Frain mostly light but with some
OL,9,Fheavier bursts mixed in. Winds still
OL,10,Fbreezy at times but remaining mild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FOutbreaks of rain slowly
OL,13,Feasing, with most parts becoming drier
OL,14,Finto the afternoon with a few bright
OL,15,Fintervals developing but also an
OL,16,Fisolated sharp shower possible. Winds
OL,17,Feasing. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
