OL,3,GLondon & South East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fwith rain Saturday morning, gradually
OL,7,Fturning brighter. Winds strengthening
OL,8,FSunday, but otherwise similar with
OL,9,Fmorning rain easing to drier
OL,10,Fconditions. Breezy Monday, but drier
OL,11,Fwith some bright spells. Mild.
